node.text:
Ayeeee. It’s time to put acai-de these tough times for abit because it’s Wonderful Wednesday!
.
@smooshasg is here to deliver some healthy goodness with their smoothie bowls! These bowls have no added sugar or flavouring! It is made with 100% fresh fruits & greens so if you’re looking for a healthy treat, these will be a good pick!

You can choose to either create your own bowl or to take your pick from the choices available! You can find them on @deliveroo_sg just by keying in their name! 
I personally like Samba because of it’s topping combination, it goes well together! 👍🏻
.
#smooshasg #smoothiebowls #deliveroosg #circuitbreakersg #leicacl #stayhomesg #stayhomeforsg
@steam.hyperpolyglot Yessss the weather is crazy. A cold dessert is best for these kinda days but alas, most dessert shops are closed. 😢

@so.gelly yah lor. Somehow 6 weeks doesn't really seem that long, but it feels rather long at the same time. 😢 Crazy times indeed. I so miss being out and about really. But nope, not going to be a covidiot. I enjoy exposing covidiots 😈🤭😝
Lookkssss so yummy!!! Especially if served chilled. Weather lately too hot liao. Driving me crazy at times. 😅🤣

@love.life.love.unicorn Haha that’s the brown one’s the Samba! I prefer it to the strawberry one. The strawberry one lacks abit of substance for the base, it’s more of a sour, refreshing kind but it’s not really acai.
I’ve never seen a brown açai bowl before! Hahah gonna save this because I will be needing it soon. I’m running out of açai at home to DIY! 😋
@mahmoudzaki1997 Thank you! You always have such kind words for me! Enjoy your day & stay safe too!
Woooow Sooooo perfectly-done and amaaaaazing photography.... I'll take the nearest bowl hahaha! Enjoy your day duuddyyyy and stay safe!
What a beauty. And your food styling game is on point! 🔥
@smooshasg My pleasure! 💕 I liked samba abit more than summer fling. 😆
❤️❤️🔥🔥 Thanks for the lovely capture and shout out @so.gelly  hope you enjoyed the bowls! 🙌
